Purpose: Filters and monitors HTTP/HTTPS traffic to your applications.
Key Features:
Protects against SQL injection, cross-site scripting (XSS), and bot traffic.
Allows creation of custom rules or use of AWS-managed rule groups.
Integrates with Amazon CloudFront, Application Load Balancer (ALB), API Gateway, AppSync, Cognito, and Amplify.
Can block, allow, or count requests based on conditions like IP, country, query strings, or headers.
Use Case Example: An e-commerce site can block bots scraping product data while allowing legitimate customers to browse.
